      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·魯頌·001.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">駉.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>駉駉牡馬，在坰之野。
薄言駉者，有驈有皇，有驪有黃，以車彭彭。
思無疆，思馬斯臧。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Fat and large are the stallions,
On the plains of the far-distant borders.
Of those stallions, fat and large,
Some are black and white-breeched; some light yellow;
Some, pure black; some, bay;
All, splendid carriage horses.
His thoughts are without limit; --
He thinks of his horses, and they are thus good.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
